{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "foodshop-api-collection",
    "name": "FoodShop API",
    "description": "REST API FoodShop - Quản lý nhà hàng, món ăn, danh mục, tin tức, đánh giá.\n\n**Biến:**\n- `base_url`: Local (mặc định http://localhost:8000)\n- `base_url_dev`: Dev/Test (https://test-site-xyz.online)\n- `token`: Bearer token (tự gán khi gọi Owner Login hoặc Admin Login)\n- **User test (khớp database/seeders/AdminUserSeeder.php):**\n  - Admin: `admin_email` / `admin_password` (admin@foodshop.com / admin123)\n  - Owner: `owner_email` / `owner_password` (owner@foodshop.com / owner123)",
    "schema": "https://schema.postman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      { "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "http://localhost:8000" },
    { "key": "base_url_dev", "value": "https://test-site-xyz.online" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "admin_email", "value": "admin@foodshop.com" },
    { "key": "admin_password", "value": "admin123" },
    { "key": "owner_email", "value": "owner@foodshop.com" },
    { "key": "owner_password", "value": "owner123" },
    { "key": "id", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "restaurantId", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "foodItemId", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "categoryId", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "code", "value": "EN" },
    { "key": "reviewId", "value": "1" }
